OL,4,Cand criticise firm over sewage leaks
OL,6,FUnhappy water customers, some who are
OL,7,Fboycotting their water bills, are
OL,8,Fgathering in Hastings today to work
OL,9,Fout how they can get Southern Water to
OL,10,Fimprove its service.
OL,12,FMany of them have protested before
OL,13,Fabout the company polluting the sea
OL,14,Fwith sewage.
OL,16,FThe company says it is investing #3
OL,17,Fbillion to find new solutions - but
OL,18,Fsome customers are still refusing to
OL,19,Fpay their full bills.
