OL,6,FThe gathering was organised by the
OL,7,FHastings Boycotts Southern Water
OL,8,F(HBSW) group,.
OL,10,FOlivia Cavanagh has been boycotting
OL,11,Fthe wastewater part of her Southern
OL,12,FWater bill for three years and has
OL,13,Fseen off several debt collection
OL,14,Fagencies over the years.
OL,16,FSpeaking on behalf of HBSW she said:
OL,17,F"New people are joining the movement
OL,18,Fall the time and the one thing that we
OL,19,Fare consistently asked is whether we
OL,20,Fcan offer support or advice.
