OL,6,FKaty Colley from boycottwaterbills.com
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is very exciting.
OL,8,FPreviously, we have been acting on our
OL,9,Fown and it is easy to feel isolated
OL,10,Fand scared, especially when you're up
OL,11,Fagainst a giant corporation
OL,12,Fthreatening you with all sorts of
OL,13,Fnasty stuff.
OL,15,F"We've been holding lots of online
OL,16,Fmeetings but getting together in
OL,17,Fperson is a wonderful way to give
OL,18,Fsupport to one another and share notes
OL,19,Fand ideas.
