OL,6,F"We have always believed that we are
OL,7,Fstronger together, and this feels like
OL,8,Fthe start of a very important journey."
OL,10,FIn November, the Consumer Council of
OL,11,FWater (CCW) released a statement
OL,12,Fregarding the issue.
OL,14,FA spokesperson said: "We're aware of
OL,15,Fsome customers who have decided to
OL,16,Fboycott paying part or all of their
OL,17,Fwater and sewerage bill in protest at
OL,18,Ftheir water company's environmental
OL,19,Fperformance.
