OL,6,F"We completely understand customers'
OL,7,Fanger and frustration on this issue.
OL,9,F"However, our advice to people who
OL,10,Fapproach us with a complaint regarding
OL,11,Fthis matter is to continue paying
OL,12,Ftheir charges.
OL,14,F"Customers who are considering
OL,15,Fboycotting payment should understand
OL,16,Fthey could face debt recovery action
OL,17,Ffrom their water company.
