OL,6,F"This could negatively impact their
OL,7,Fcredit rating and also potentially
OL,8,Fresult in additional costs being added
OL,9,Fto their bill."
OL,11,FThe spokesperson for CCW continued:
OL,12,F"There is no requirement for a water
OL,13,Fcompany to suspend or delay debt
OL,14,Frecovery action just because a
OL,15,Fcustomer has raised a dispute with
OL,16,Fthem or CCW.
