OL,6,F"Ofwat's Paying Fair guidance only
OL,7,Fapplies where a water company is
OL,8,Finvestigating the accuracy of a
OL,9,Fcustomer's bill or whether it has been
OL,10,Fpaid. This is not relevant here as
OL,11,Fcustomers are choosing to boycott bill
OL,12,Fpayment.
OL,14,F"Any issues that customers want to
OL,15,Fraise about the performance of water
OL,16,Fcompanies should be raised with the
OL,17,Fcompany directly in the first
OL,18,Finstance, and ` if concerns remain
OL,19,Funresolved ` Ofwat, the Environment
OL,20,FAgency or Natural Resources Wales as
OL,21,Fappropriate."
